<br>
He will give you the 10-item chest when you spout the correct words.  You put your ten rods in the chest, hit combine (to my knowledge, you can't fail on this), and viola, you will have both the staff and eyes in your possession.<br>
<br>
To get the runes for Ice Comet, you must hand in both the staff and eyes.  That's the only thing you'd hand in either item for. <p><i><b><font face="ARIAL" size="2" color="#FF0000">
