<br>
The hardest rods to obtain (above mentioned aside) is the one in Lake Rathe.  I got lucky on that one and grabbed it while a group was camping whatever spawn it is that sees through invis.<br>
<br>
The DW Goblns in oasis don't see through invis...you can just go invis and drop in to grab the rod...works well.<br>
<br>
The other rod that may be hard to get is in Neriak...I had a friend lead me back when I was like level 12 or something to get that one...couldn't find it again if I wanted to I think.<br>
<br>
as for the Eurids Crossing rod, the only sharks I saw were so far away from the boat that you would have had to try real hard to agro them.  Just swim down a littl ways till the the seabed flattens out and look around a bit - can't miss it.  Also I think it was night time when I tried, and I've heard a rumor that the sharks DON'T swim the holding pattern at night....<br>
<br>
good luck <p><P></P>
