<br>
Oasis : Piece of cake. None of the gobbies saw thru invis. However, some caster types can spawn and they will see thru invis. Always con before going in the tower to get rod.<br>
<br>
Everfrost : Get enduring breath, swim thru tunnel, waltz in and get the rod. Not a single icebone attacked. All I had on was regular invis.<br>
<br>
Rathe : Died once on this one. Get enduring breath and invis on. Tunnel is at approximately pos 2600, pos 1425. It's long and extremely dark. Just go straight in the middle of it and you'll run into a tower. First time, I was about to grab it and a dw gobbie saw thru invis and ripped me a new one. Second time, had a guildmate (55 bard) help me. We just swam in and grabbed it with reg invis on. Nothing attacked. I think I was unlucky the first time - caster gobbie must've spawned and has see invis on.<br>
<br>
Erud's Xing : As I've stated before, swim in and get it at night. Most likely won't be a shark there.<br>
<br>
Others are a piece of cake including Neriak. Invis, walk thru 1st gate and jump in water to the left.<br>
<br>
I'm praying that I don't die more than 3 times for the Lguk one...<br>
<br>
Faz<br>
still 29 Wiz.<br>
